href=\"#vps-queue-restart\"\u003evps_queue_restart\u003c/a\u003e function calls.\u003cbr\u003e\nSome VPS types also allow you to use the \u003ca href=\"#vps-screenshot\"\u003evps_screenshot\u003c/a\u003e function to get a screenshot of whats currently on the VPS's screen.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e\n\u003ca id=\"purchasing-a-vps\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#purchasing-a-vps\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"octicon octicon-link\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003ePurchasing a VPS\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe VPS order process is broken down into 2 functions.\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter choosing the order parameters, you must first make a call to \u003ca href=\"#validate-buy-vps\"\u003evalidate_buy_vps\u003c/a\u003e to check for any problems in the parameters.\u003cbr\u003e\nThe function will respond with an array containing an updated set of parameters (if any of them needed changed) and additional fields telling you if the order details were ok or a description of what problems there were in the order. \u003cbr\u003e\nIt also will return with sevral fields telling you how much it will cost initially , how much it will cost each time you are billed after the initial signup, and how often you are billed.\u003cbr\u003e\nWhen you get an 'ok' as the 'status' response you can pass the parameters to the \u003ca href=\"#buy-vps\"\u003ebuy_vps\u003c/a\u003e function to place the order.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThis function will also return a status field with 'ok' if the order was placed properly or 'error' otherwise and a description of any problems in status_text.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e\n\u003ca id=\"vps-server-locations\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#vps-server-locations\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"octicon octicon-link\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003eVPS Server Locations\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOur more popular VPS types are available in multiple locations.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nYou should probably choose the location closest to you or your clients.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nTo get a list of the current locations use the \u003ca href=\"#get_vps_locations_array\"\u003eget_vps_locations_array\u003c/a\u003e function.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nOur primary datacenter location is in Secaucus, NJ (location id 1) and is probably the best choice if unsure what to choose.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nSome of the VPS types might only be available at that location as well.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e\n\u003ca id=\"vps-types-and-pricing\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#vps-types-and-pricing\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"octicon octicon-link\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003eVPS Types and Pricing\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe have several types of Servers available for use with VPS Hosting. \u003cbr\u003e\nYou can get a list of the types available and there cost per slice/unit by making a call to the \u003ca href=\"#get_vps_slice_types\"\u003eget_vps_slice_types\u003c/a\u003e function.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAdditionally you can get a list of the vps platforms with the \u003ca href=\"#get_vps_platforms_array\"\u003eget_vps_platforms_array\u003c/a\u003e function.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e\n\u003ca id=\"vps-details\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#vps-details\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"octicon octicon-link\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003eVPS Details\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo get a list of all your current VPS's you can use the \u003ca href=\"#vps-get-services\"\u003evps_get_services\u003c/a\u003e function and \u003ca href=\"#vps-get-service\"\u003evps_get_service\u003c/a\u003e to get all the details for a given VPS.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e\n\u003ca id=\"buy-vps-admin\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#buy-vps-admin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"octicon
